QTitle: If you could choose one place to live forever where would you live?

QAnswers.AnsText: In an apartment overlooking the Eiffel Tower

QTitle: What's your idea of a perfect day?

QAnswers.AnsText: Spending the day out shopping for all new souvenirs
Enjoying all the finest dining and three course meals I can
Isolated and enjoying the beauty of nature

QTitle: Which of these describes you best?

QAnswers.AnsText: I like to go to only the finest dining and shopping centers when I travel
I like to splurge on vacation but within reason
My favorite thing is to find a great deal
My motto is the more free the better the experience
